programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents KOK '84 World Series from Vilnius Lithuania part 2. In this episode, watch as Ukrainian Volodymyr Hynzhu takes on Lithuanian Raimondas Avlasevicius, Finn Larsen (Ireland) goes up against the more experienced Nauris Lukosiunas (Lithuania) and Oleskil Mykhailo 9-0 (Ukraine) faces Henrikas Viksraitis 43-7(Lithuania). In the main event Lithuanians Zygimantas Ramaska and Vitoldas Jagelo face one another in an MMA Bushido battle with at title on the line.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 257 - Shamrock FC 334
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents Shamrock Fighting Championship out of the Ameristar Casino in St. Charles, MO. In this event Austin Miller faces Arvin Mills in the cage, Arnez Ferguson takes on Pat Vega in a kickboxing bout and in a female match, Livvy Pecher takes on Lora Campbell. Also Jason Gavril faces Isaac Dancy and Nico Alcaraz takes on Todd Madden in the middleweight division. In the Co-Main event Devin Anderson takes on Aushton Elleby Midkiff and in the main event Jeremiah Curtright with a 3 fight win streak takes on Zack Davis with a 4 fight win streak.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 258 - UFA Presents the Fighter's Only World MMA Awards XIII
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents the 13th annual Fighter's Only 2021 World MMA Awards from Worre Studios in Las Vegas, hosted by Chael Sonnen. Presentations by Dave Farra, Jessy Jess, Doggface208, Emily Whitmire, Cassie Scherbo, Jay Hieron, Dan Henderson, Kayla Harrison, Mackenzie Dern, and more.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 259 - KOK 94 Tallinn Part 1
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents King of Kings 94 World Series from Tallinn, Estonia part 1. Young Estonian fighters Stanislav Teniugin and Siim Viljus battle under KOK Kickboxing rules. Aleh Moshin from Belarus takes on Karl Margus Haud out of Estonia and Edvinas Bubelis (Lithuania) faces Sergei Strinza (Estonia). Also, powerhouse Volodymyr Hynzju from Ukraine takes on Aleksey Larin from Estonia.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 260 - KOK 94 Tallinn Part 2
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents King of Kings 94 World Series from Tallinn, Estonia part 2. Watch as the first ever KOK women's bantamweight world championship title is on the line. In some intense all-female matchups each fighter is vying to move on to the finals for a chance at the title. In the semi-finals Estonians Sigrid Kapanen and Astrid Johanna Grents fight to move on and Italian Ludovica Ciarpaglini faces Polish Ilona Woijda to see who will move on to the Grand Prix final match and have a chance at the title.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 261 - KOK 94 Tallinn Part 3
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents King of Kings 94 World Series from Tallinn, Estonia part 3. Watch as Canadian Mohammed Shushan faces Jevgeni "Zora XXL" Ravlusevits of Estonia and Dzmitry Varats (Belarus) takes on Ott Remmer (Estonia).

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 262 - Shamrock FC 335
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents Shamrock 335 from Ameristar Casino St Charles. In this event Austin Miller faces Arvin Mills in the cage, Arnez Ferguson takes on Pat Vega in a kickboxing bout and in a female match, Livvy Pecher takes on Lora Campbell. Also Jason Gavril faces Isaac Dancy and Nico Alcaraz takes on Todd Madden in the middleweight division. In the Co-Main event Devin Anderson takes on Aushton Elleby Midkiff and in the main event Jeremiah Curtright with a 3 fight win streak takes on Zack Davis with a 4 fight win streak.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 258 - UFA Presents the Fighter's Only World MMA Awards XIII
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents the 13th annual Fighter's Only 2021 World MMA Awards from Worre Studios in Las Vegas, hosted by Chael Sonnen. Presentations by Dave Farra, Jessy Jess, Doggface208, Emily Whitmire, Cassie Scherbo, Jay Hieron, Dan Henderson, Kayla Harrison, Mackenzie Dern, and more.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 259 - KOK 94 Tallinn Part 1
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents King of Kings 94 World Series from Tallinn, Estonia part 1. Young Estonian fighters Stanislav Teniugin and Siim Viljus battle under KOK Kickboxing rules. Aleh Moshin from Belarus takes on Karl Margus Haud out of Estonia and Edvinas Bubelis (Lithuania) faces Sergei Strinza (Estonia). Also, powerhouse Volodymyr Hynzju from Ukraine takes on Aleksey Larin from Estonia.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 260 - KOK 94 Tallinn Part 2
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents King of Kings 94 World Series from Tallinn, Estonia part 2. Watch as the first ever KOK women's bantamweight world championship title is on the line. In some intense all-female matchups each fighter is vying to move on to the finals for a chance at the title. In the semi-finals Estonians Sigrid Kapanen and Astrid Johanna Grents fight to move on and Italian Ludovica Ciarpaglini faces Polish Ilona Woijda to see who will move on to the Grand Prix final match and have a chance at the title.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 261 - KOK 94 Tallinn Part 3
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents King of Kings 94 World Series from Tallinn, Estonia part 3. Watch as Canadian Mohammed Shushan faces Jevgeni "Zora XXL" Ravlusevits of Estonia and Dzmitry Varats (Belarus) takes on Ott Remmer (Estonia).

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 262 - Shamrock FC 335
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents Shamrock 335 from Ameristar Casino St Charles. Watch as Pat Gordon takes on Adam Stone, Stanton Ketcherside faces Jerry Ing, Matt Tinker battles it out against James Yarbrough, Kevin Mueller faces Trevon Crawford and Tavae Lewis faces Josh Weston In the co-main event in a kickboxing bout, Ian Zarvos faces Cody Naucke and in the main event Josh Augustin returns to the cage after a long layoff to take on blackbelt Thomas Thatcher.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 263 - SFT 30 - Predador vs Manchinha
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents SFT 30 from Brazil. Denis Araujo with 6 KO's meets Jose Reborn Alexandre in the cage for a fierce MMA bout. In a compelling matchup, Paulo Pizzo takes on the much younger Fernando "ben 10" Lourenco and in the lightweight division #1 ranked Felipe Buakaw takes on #2 Marcio Velaminho. In the main event Wellington Predador faces Thiago Manchinha in an exciting matchup.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 255 - KOK’84 World Series, Vilnius part 1
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents KOK '84 World Series from Vilnius Lithuania part 1. In a battle between Lithuanian fighters, Zygimantas Kidikas making his pro debut goes up against his 2-0 opponent Ovidijus Pocius. Watch as Aleh Moshin (Belarus) faces Samuelis Sorochovas (Lithuania), Osvaladas Fedorovic takes on the less experienced Aurimas Krukauskas in a battle between Lithuanian fighters and Vladislav Shatunskui (Poland) battles against Gustas Dimsa (Lithuania). programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 256 - KOK’84 World Series, Vilnius Part 2
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents KOK '84 World Series from Vilnius Lithuania part 2. In this episode, watch as Ukrainian Volodymyr Hynzhu takes on Lithuanian Raimondas Avlasevicius, Finn Larsen (Ireland) goes up against the more experienced Nauris Lukosiunas (Lithuania) and Oleskil Mykhailo 9-0 (Ukraine) faces Henrikas Viksraitis 43-7(Lithuania). In the main event Lithuanians Zygimantas Ramaska and Vitoldas Jagelo face one another in an MMA Bushido battle with at title on the line.

Young Estonian fighters Stanislav Teniugin and Siim Viljus battle under KOK Kickboxing rules. Aleh Moshin from Belarus takes on Karl Margus Haud out of Estonia and Edvinas Bubelis (Lithuania) faces Sergei Strinza (Estonia). Also, powerhouse Volodymyr Hynzju from Ukraine takes on Aleksey Larin from Estonia.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 260 - KOK 94 Tallinn Part 2
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents King of Kings 94 World Series from Tallinn, Estonia part 2. Watch as the first ever KOK women's bantamweight world championship title is on the line. In some intense all-female matchups each fighter is vying to move on to the finals for a chance at the title. In the semi-finals Estonians Sigrid Kapanen and Astrid Johanna Grents fight to move on and Italian Ludovica Ciarpaglini faces Polish Ilona Woijda to see who will move on to the Grand Prix final match and have a chance at the title.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 255 - KOK’84 World Series, Vilnius part 1
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents KOK '84 World Series from Vilnius Lithuania part 1. In a battle between Lithuanian fighters, Zygimantas Kidikas making his pro debut goes up against his 2-0 opponent Ovidijus Pocius. Watch as Aleh Moshin (Belarus) faces Samuelis Sorochovas (Lithuania), Osvaladas Fedorovic takes on the less experienced Aurimas Krukauskas in a battle between Lithuanian fighters and Vladislav Shatunskui (Poland) battles against Gustas Dimsa (Lithuania). In addition Polish fighter Hubert Dylewski takes on Lithuanian Jan Naus in a very evenly matched fight.

programme.title: United Fight Alliance - UFA 256 - KOK’84 World Series, Vilnius Part 2
programme.desc: United Fight Alliance presents KOK '84 World Series from Vilnius Lithuania part 2. In this episode, watch as Ukrainian Volodymyr Hynzhu takes on Lithuanian Raimondas Avlasevicius, Finn Larsen (Ireland) goes up against the more experienced Nauris Lukosiunas (Lithuania) and Oleskil Mykhailo 9-0 (Ukraine) faces Henrikas Viksraitis 43-7(Lithuania). In the main event Lithuanians Zygimantas Ramaska and Vitoldas Jagelo face one another in an MMA Bushido battle with at title on the line.

programme.title: The New Guest
programme.desc: When a man and woman check into a remote cabin to complete a therapy exercise, they soon realize they will encounter more than they bargained for.

programme.title: Boy in the Corner
programme.desc: The backward system of society pushes another dream-filled boy to the curb, with his aspiration suppressed, he is at risk of falling into the attractive arms of gang life.

programme.title: New Man Pending
programme.desc: After a terrible five-year relationship, a woman begins picking up the pieces of her life. Her new business partner falls for her, but her old love won’t let go.

programme.title: Pattern
programme.desc: A few months after the maternal death of his partner, a man is at a crossroads on how to raise their baby.

programme.title: American Wisper
programme.desc: A previously respected Black businessman in New Jersey is suspected of murdering his family and films his own investigation into the crimes to prove his innocence. Based on actual events.

programme.title: The Great Divide
programme.desc: At a monthly gathering of her friends, a student of the Tantra and Kama Sutra introduces an unusual game designed to elicit the feelings and impressions men and women have about one another.

programme.title: Never Heard
programme.desc: Aaron Davis is accused of murder for a crime he didn’t commit. His son Jalen gets entangled with dangerous drug dealers. Will Aaron find a way to prove his innocence and save his son’s life before it is too late?

programme.title: When It Comes Around
programme.desc: A young successful sports executive falls in love with a new agent at his office. He is manipulated by this beautiful woman and used as a pawn for her advancement.

programme.title: F*cking Married
programme.desc: LJ and Candice, get married overnight but before a judge can grant an annulment they are sentenced to live together for 30 days under the same roof.

programme.title: They’re Trying to Kill Us
programme.desc: Why do people of color suffer from disproportionately higher rates of chronic disease? From producers Chris Paul and Billie Eilish, this film investigates the link between diet, disease, poverty, racism, and corruption, unraveling what keeps us sick.

programme.title: Popolo
programme.desc: A Special Forces officer lands in Hawaii to fulfill his best friend’s dream, who was killed in action. Turning a property in a seedy part of O’ahu into Mixed Martial Arts Academy brings problems involving racism, forbidden love and the notorious Yakuza!

programme.title: As Evil Does
programme.desc: When a door-to-door Evangelist unknowingly enters the home of an atheist, the two find themselves trapped inside a dark, sinister evil where all hell breaks loose, and to survive they must fight against supernatural forces.

programme.title: You're Hired!
programme.desc: The race to the top isn't black and white when co-workers are tricked into believing their skin color will impact a major job promotion, and sabotage is the fast track to success.

programme.title: They Live In The Shadows
programme.desc: A husband and wife have separated after a tragedy strains their marriage. After one isn't heard from for an extended period of time, the other goes and discovers a terrifying occurrence.

programme.title: The Crip Who Loves Yoga
programme.desc: Two men: one a Crip gangster who ran the block selling drugs, the other a Native American biker, take the hero's journey against great odds and change their destiny and that of their communities, with yoga.

programme.title: Dirty
programme.desc: In Atlanta, family and the streets don't mix. Lies lead to hate, and jealousy can get you killed.

programme.title: CainAbel
programme.desc: In this modern retelling of the Cain and Abel story, a family is torn apart by a father's reckless decision to borrow money from a notorious drug dealer, leading to deadly consequences and a battle of good versus evil between his sons Cain and Abel.

programme.title: Sisters and The Shrink 2
programme.desc: Sisters and the Shrink 2 is a comedy that touches on real-life challenges. The six women try to navigate their lives with their significant others and family but still fall short of the true happines they desire. The shrink is their only hope.

programme.title: Crooked
programme.desc: After his brother is wrongfully framed for murder, Detective Jackson King takes the law into his own hands to bring down the Nefarious Kingpin responsible.

programme.title: Haiti Speaks
programme.desc: Haiti Speaks uncovers what neither centuries of colonialism, debt, discrimination or natural disaster could destroy: The depth of the Haitian spirit. Call it pride. Call it spirit. Call it hope. Whatever it is, you feel it in Haiti Speaks.

programme.title: In the Moment
programme.desc: A hilarious comedy about different cultures, the struggles of acting, and life in the big city. After being accepted into renowned actor Matt Turner's acting class, a sheltered, small-town girl, moves to the city to pursue her dream of acting.

programme.title: Love by Accident
programme.desc: While on a road trip, Daphne and her godmother Fran get into an accident. Wanting to keep Fran off the road, Daphne enlists their mechanic, Matthew, as her fake boyfriend. But soon, their fake relationship will not be so fake after all.

programme.title: Joyland
programme.desc: Pooda Johnson is celebrating his last weekend on house arrest with a kickback (party) that could jeopardize the very freedom he’s celebrating.

programme.title: Concealed Secrets
programme.desc: After their mother's death, 3 sisters go on a dysfunctional rollercoaster ride of lies, deceit and betrayal.

programme.title: Story of Her
programme.desc: "Story of Her" is a 2022 dynamic American documentary that showcases bold stories of struggle and triumphs in the lives of everyday women.

programme.title: Jimmy's Friends
programme.desc: After a five year stint in prison, Jimmy Tucker returns to the streets of Oakland to find his entire life destroyed and everyone else doing well. With zero prospects and nothing to his name, Jimmy only wants one thing: his cut from the heist.

programme.title: Forever Loved
programme.desc: After getting out of an abusive relationship, Alexis has her guard up. Her newest client Devin Scott falls for her and shows her what love is.

programme.title: Bosses
programme.desc: "Bosses," is a film about a leader of a brutal criminal organization who is given seven days to leave town or die. Now he must race against time to find out who wants him dead.

programme.title: Dormant
programme.desc: Detective Jordan Long goes undercover to investigate kidnappings in a quiet neighborhood.

programme.title: The Day I Had to Grow Up
programme.desc: The Day I Had To Grow Up is a documentary featuring six activists & the events that shaped their political lives.

programme.title: Six Rounds
programme.desc: Ex-boxer fights old friend after drug deal goes wrong

programme.title: The Pastor and Mrs. Jones
programme.desc: Pastor reassures soon-to-be wife, church deacons concerned

programme.title: My King
programme.desc: Man's mother interferes with perfect relationship

programme.title: Keeping Secrets: Director's Cut
programme.desc: When a known serial killer reemerges, a woman is thrust into action with a call from a childhood friend. Determined to prove herself, Sam, must go undercover to catch a serial killer.

programme.title: Black Serial Killers: Truth or Fiction
programme.desc: America's fixated on serial killers, yet ignores those like Samuel Little,with more victims, because they're black. This bold documentary confronts this media blind spot, backed by criminal justice expert Allan Branson.

programme.title: Detroit Ransom
programme.desc: Parents of a 14-year-old prodigy will stop at nothing to rescue their daughter from a ruthless Detroit crime lord who holds her for Ransom.

programme.title: Behind the Veil
programme.desc: To the community, Stacey and Darrel are models of hope, success and strength. Behind closed doors, addiction and betrayal are ripping them apart.

programme.title: Hream
programme.desc: Join Doug Hream Blunt, male nurse, and adult music student, as he embarks on a world tour, partnering with young music students and professionals.

programme.title: KeKe
programme.desc: Keke is an ordinary schoolgirl who loves playing with her friend at the park until, one day, she is tragically killed. Driven by pain and longing, Keke’s tortured spirit reaches out from beyond the grave to get revenge on her killers.

programme.title: Bleeding Butterfly
programme.desc: Twin sisters’ love for each other is threatened when a dark secret from the past seeks to destroy the love the family shares. Lies told to protect the family are about to destroy them.

programme.title: Hypno
programme.desc: The lines are blurred between illusion and reality as a struggling writer takes on a psychological journey that lands himself caught between a mysterious love affair and unresolved issues from the past.

programme.title: The Send Off
programme.desc: 17 year old Nya goes into her 12th grade year with high hopes for senior prom but is quickly brought to reality after finding out about her dad's incarceration and her mom's disturbing past.

programme.title: Where Hearts Lie
programme.desc: A young Brooklyn real estate mogul in the making gambles his success, sanity, and the safety of his young son when falling for the wrong woman.

programme.title: Men Love Lust
programme.desc: Akin had it all: a perfect family and a thriving business. But one encounter changed everything, leading him down an unforeseen path.

programme.title: Car Lot Comedy
programme.desc: When an injury crushes a man's dreams of playing Major League baseball, he finds a new line of work at a dubious used car lot.

programme.title: Emergency Contact
programme.desc: A comedy about a single black female in her 30s whose tired of having to list her mother as her Emergency Contact. This saucy hopeless romantic tries every trick in the book to avoid remaining alone and single.

programme.title: Paper Line
programme.desc: Seven pledges get the shock of a lifetime when they unknowingly sign up to join the secret fraternity of black martial artists at an HBCU in Florida.

programme.title: Death Rot
programme.desc: A heavy metal band are on tour when their bus breaks down in a remote area. They encounter a God-worshipping family who funds their church by selling meat for profit - human meat.

programme.title: Saving Grace
programme.desc: Grace is a young nurse who lives a life of pain and anguish. Her addiction to heroin has forced the authorities to take away her beloved daughter Jessica. But she seems to find solace when approached by an odd survivalist named Clayton.

programme.title: The Vampire Project
programme.desc: When two young and ambitious filmmakers Michael and Michelle decide to sneak hidden video cameras into the illegal world of Manhattan's underground after hours clubs, Michelle is targeted by a charming vampire named Adrian.

programme.title: Real Cases of Shadow People: The Sarah McCormick Story
programme.desc: Three students went missing in October 2018: Sarah McCormick, Kyle Miller, and Joseph Moore.

programme.title: Dream Nightmare
programme.desc: A Manny Velazquez Psychological Thriller about a young detective finds a handcrafted Indian sculpture in an alley, and takes it home with him, but he soon realizes that the sculpture is bringing his worst fears to life.

programme.title: Bleeding Through
programme.desc: After the death of her parents, Lindsey still struggles with overwhelming grief. Her only outlet is a newfound romance but when it turns to vicious betrayal Lindsey unearths a capacity for violence and bloody revenge from beyond the grave!

programme.title: The Woods of Purgatory
programme.desc: A priest recovering from the death of his mother is targeted by a mysterious cult on Halloween.

programme.title: Undead Apocalypse
programme.desc: A bio-attack by terrorists causes a sudden zombie outbreak. A small group of survivors at a university struggles to reach a professor's lab where a possible cure to the pathogen resides.

programme.title: Survival Instinct
programme.desc: Taking its cue from classic survival-thrillers such as 'Duel' and 'Deliverance', 'Survival Instinct' is a fast-paced edge-of-your-seat thriller with a strong female lead and a plausible, morally-ambiguous villain.

programme.title: Dead End: Zombie Apocalypse
programme.desc: After a deadly plague rapidly wipes out humanity and transforms the dead into walking dead, a small band of survivors documents their fight for survival through the lens of a camera, capturing what could be their last few days alive.

programme.title: The Last Light: An Irish Ghost Story
programme.desc: Handy man Rob is hired to seal up an abandoned mansion along the Irish coast. But Rob feels he's not alone. Is it kids playing a joke? Or a force that does not wish to be disturbed...

programme.title: The House on Mansfield Street: Evil Next Door
programme.desc: James seeks a fresh start at Anthony's house on Mansfield Street, but unsettling sounds of violent fights from the supposedly empty neighboring house disrupt his peace, plunging him into a supernatural mystery.

programme.title: Nightshift
programme.desc: On her first day working as an assistant to a pathologist, a young woman is stuck in the morgue when the dead begin to manifest signs of resurrection.

programme.title: Werewolf Cabal
programme.desc: An American horror author travels to a small rural town in the UK. During his stay, he uncovers a cabal of locals who worship Werewolves!

programme.title: Dark Entities
programme.desc: Following an accident in 1977, the Winters siblings inherit a mysterious house holding dark secrets that seek to threaten everything they hold dear.

programme.title: They're Outside
programme.desc: While filming a documentary, a YouTube celebrity psychologist attempts to convince an agoraphobic woman to leave her home in just 10 days. As time starts to run out, Pagan rituals, dark fairytales, and folklore soon become a horrifying reality.

programme.title: Distort

programme.title: Reel Nightmare: Book of Nightmare
programme.desc: Three beautiful, vengeful witches awakened by an ancient book, the Necronomicon, bring production of a film in their old family home to a deadly halt.

programme.title: Reel Nightmare: Book of Nightmare
programme.desc: Three beautiful, vengeful witches awakened by an ancient book, the Necronomicon, bring production of a film in their old family home to a deadly halt.

programme.title: Sadomaster
programme.desc: Extreme urban violence reigns in Argentina. Senator Beccar Varela rises as the only way to stop violence with his "zero tolerance" politic. People doesn't suspect that Beccar is the head of the nazi gang that causes the violence. When members of the gang torture and rape a retarded man, a mysterious Masked avenger begins his brutal revenge against the gangs and the corrupt politics.

programme.title: Domestic Hell
programme.desc: Jack and Julia are a couple with dark secrets. Blanca is a tortured soul with a past. And Olivia is hellbent on finding the truth. When these four lives intersect, nobody escapes. Bonds are tested; wills are broken; and, metal is forged. It's a tale of survival, trust, and darkness from the creators of Bloody Drama.

programme.title: Satan Claus
programme.desc: With the clock ticking and the body count rising, Homicide Detective Timothy Reynolds reluctantly volunteers to assist his former partner, Detective Alan Fryer, with the investigation to a slew of grisly murders left behind by a mission orientated killer during the Christmas holidays.

programme.title: Beware the Boogeyman
programme.desc: Dr. Tristian Mackenzie makes her way to a Psychiatric Hospital for the criminally insane, where she learns of the strange series of cases from Dr. Moon.

programme.title: The Edison Death Machine
programme.desc: Thought only to exist in legend, Edison's device for contacting the dead is found...and stolen. A group of professional thieves go on a global crime spree reanimating the dead in order to steal treasures thought long lost. Things begin to go wrong when they cannot control the creatures, and the machine begins to develop a mind of its own.

programme.title: Death of A Ghost Hunter
programme.desc: Based on true events, a ghost hunter Carter Simms is paid to conduct a paranormal investigation of a suspected haunted house. Along with a cameraman, a reporter, and a spiritual advocate, she embarks on a three night journey into terror.

programme.title: Chain of Souls
programme.desc: When a naive aspiring actress from Podunk, Texas disappears in Los Angeles, her protective sister comes looking for her. The clues lead her to a diabolical cult masquerading as a theater group and the fight of her life.

programme.title: Infliction
programme.desc: In 2011, two brothers documented their murder spree in North Carolina. This is the actual assembled footage.

programme.title: Blood Punch
programme.desc: A young man breaks out of rehab to follow a mysterious girl into an easy drug score. But when she lures him to an isolated cabin, their simple love triangle quickly descends into a mind-blowing cycle of carnage and mayhem with no escape.

programme.title: Dirty Conscience
programme.desc: A cop thriller from Chile.Two young police recruits are assigned a tough, decorated Officer to train them. It quickly becomes clear that their new boss is involved with serious corruption. At first the two young cops try to look the other way. But as their boss begins to doubt their loyalty, the two recruits must choose between saving their honor and their careers--before their boss has them killed.

programme.title: Beyond the Night
programme.desc: When a soldier's son reveals damning information about a local gangster's missing daughter, a war of attrition wreaks havoc on their forgotten coal mining town.

programme.title: Haunted Boat
programme.desc: HAUNTED BOAT is a mystical, mind-twisting psychological horror film about six teenagers going on a boat trip and getting lost in parallel dimensions where they have to face their greatest fears.

programme.title: Insidious Inferno
programme.desc: A secluded cottage is plagued by a series of gruesome murders, unbeknownst to the inhabitants something other worldly lurks within the halls.

programme.title: Point of Fear
programme.desc: When Mark, Parker, Melissa, and Karen decide to go camping in the small town of Pleasant Point, they find the town has much to offer... including a string of brutal murders.

programme.title: Almost Invisible
programme.desc: Be captured by the Invisible. To ease the weight of their college workload, unsuspecting teenagers seize the opportunity to to turn their end-of-the-summer party, into a sick, house wrecking.

programme.title: Holistay
programme.desc: Two couples, who do not know each other, double book a vacation house in San Diego and strange events begin to happen. "Things are not as they appear."

programme.title: Antisocial Behaviour
programme.desc: Jakob Kelser is a man with a horrific, troubled past. Having been failed by society and plagued by a gruesome childhood memory, he is forced to live alone in the unholy hell of God's making.

programme.title: Pillow Party Massacre
programme.desc: Haunted by a prank gone fatally wrong, five friends reunite to heal. But not all can forget, and it's clear that someone or something is out for revenge.

programme.title: Weekend Killer
programme.desc: Detective's Joey Moretti and Patricia Stevens are trying to track down a serial killer that preys on young attractive women, leaving only cryptic messages carved into their flesh as clues! Joey struggles to keep himself together as the investigation leads him closer and closer to the deranged killer!

programme.title: The Faith Community
programme.desc: A group of religious students drive into the remote wilderness to spend time with a religious sect and strengthen their bond with God. The three unsuspecting students film everything to document their experience but soon find themselves in the dark.

programme.title: A Gun for Jennifer
programme.desc: A woman comes to New York City from Ohio to escape an abusive husband and gets entangled with murderous female vigilantes who prey on abusive men.

programme.title: Cut Her Out
programme.desc: Darcy can't purge her mind of the animalistic abuse she suffered as a child at the hands of her mother. Darcy's therapist Ryan discovers that her family homestead has been abandoned.

People who started out from meager beginnings or limited education, to become very wealthy! Many of these people are among us and act no differently than we do, but they have a success story to tell and tricks of success to share. These are the people profiled in “Titans of Business”.

programme.title: Sailing To Tokyo - Episode 2
programme.desc: In this episode we are following the 2019 RSX European Championships. The 2019 RS:X Europeans and Youth European Championships which are being held on the island of Mallorca, Spain, is a record turn out for the RS:X Class with 333 confirmed entries from 43 different nations representing six different continents over five days of racing. This is not a challenge for the class and athletes alone, but also for the local host Club Nautic Arenal.

programme.title: Rolex New York Yacht Invitational Cup - Highlight
Gulf of Mexico
programme.desc: Beppe Faresin is an extreme kayaker with a dream: venturing into the Gulf of Mexico on a kayak. In this adventure, he will kayak his way through the Mexican lagoons and swamps to discover the wild nature of this unique country. Faresin is already famous for raising funds for UNICEF while paddling in rivers and oceans all over the world. Now, he faces a new challenge: crossing the Gulf of Mexico by himself. For almost 1500 km, this apparently fearless athlete will discover corners of Mexico otherwise unreachable by land. Follow his challenge navigating through the Gulf and find out what happens along the way.

programme.title: Kite Masters - Episode 5
programme.desc: There are two elements that grabbed our attention during the 2020 Formula Kite Mixed Relay European Championships: the UK’s Connor Bainbridge and the Polish team.Along with his teammate Elli Aldridge, Connor managed to defend his European title. Meanwhile, the Polish team was the great surprise of the championship, having two out of their six teams qualifying to the gold fleet. After that, we will focus on the Kite venues hosting the hottest action from the kite events.We will discover why riders love these locations and what makes the International Kiteboarding Association so confident in the venues. Finally, we reencounter four-time world champion, Daniela Moroz, who shared some more golden Kiteboarding tips.

programme.title: Kite Masters - Episode 6
programme.desc: As we come to the end of the 2020 series, we'll take a look back over all the happenings earlier this season in the extreme world of kiteboarding as well as the transformation of the sport on the road to Paris 2024.Later on, we are set to find out what happened during the last event of the season, the 2020 KiteFoil European Championships taking place in Playa de las Burras, Gran Canaria, Spain. We end our journey travelling to the USA to meet one of the most popular riders in the world: Daniela Moroz.

programme.title: Anchored in Paradise - Ep.6 - NIN - PAG
Atlantic Cup - Episode 2
programme.desc: The second leg of the race goes from New York City to New Port City, Rhode Island. There are two major challenges on this leg: one is getting out of New York Harbour, dealing with the tides and the thicker winds that come off the city, and the other is dealing with the commercial traffic, as it is one of the busiest ports in the world. How will the skippers manage?

Transat Panerai Classique
programme.desc: World Champion Kitesurfer and Nautical Channel host, Bruno Sroka travels to Martinique to welcome the gems of the sea from their Atlantic crossing. Witness some of the most extraordinary yachts ever built and have fun seeing Bruno take the sea on both a traditional Martinique Yoles boat and a Classic European one. This will be the first Olympic class racing event to take place in the UK since 2016! Are you coming with us?

programme.title: Reaching Reality - Episode 1 - Origin
programme.desc: From under the Golden Gate Bridge down to the Santa Cruz Islands the three friends and their little boat are now heading south. However bad weather is on the horizon and signs that the film and the filmmaker are already thinking about abandoning ship are starting to leak through. After a long night of sea sickness, it’s time to face reality and see who’s going to stick around and who’s going to go.

programme.title: Formula Wing European Championships - Ep.1 - URLA
New York - Vendée Transatlantic Race
programme.desc: This single-handed yacht race will cross the Northern Atlantic through two symbolic cities: New York and Sables d’Olonne. The departure from the Big Apple represents a cosmopolitan crossroad of influences, as well as the cradle of the IMOCA Class, while the arrival in the Sables d’Olonne means landing in the Old Continent after days or weeks of harsh conditions.After crossing a risky and challenging course straight through the middle of the “iceberg alley”, the skippers will arrive in the heart of the Vendée Globe considered as the “Everest of the Sea”. The Transatlantic race is the final event of the IMOCA Globe Series and it allows racers to build their hard racing miles. It represents a further opportunity to reinforce its image as a marine region, thus it is an awaited event for all those sailors thinking about embarking on the Vendée Globe.Follow their journey from New York to Sables d’Olonne in New York – Vendée Transatlantic Race. Available on Nautical Channel.

programme.title: Under the Hull - Under the Hull
Anchored in Paradise - Ep.7 - NOVALJA - RAB
Atlantic Cup - Episode 3
programme.desc: Welcome back to this edition of the Atlantic Cup. It is time for the third and final leg of the competition, the inshore series. Dragon and Gryphon Solo 2 are tied for, and teams have added 4 extra crew, allowing them to push their boats around the tight courses in Naragannset Bay. Any mistake could be the difference between first and last. Who will become the winner in this edition?

programme.title: Gulf of Mexico
programme.desc: Beppe Faresin is an extreme kayaker with a dream: venturing into the Gulf of Mexico on a kayak. In this adventure, he will kayak his way through the Mexican lagoons and swamps to discover the wild nature of this unique country. Faresin is already famous for raising funds for UNICEF while paddling in rivers and oceans all over the world. Now, he faces a new challenge: crossing the Gulf of Mexico by himself. For almost 1500 km, this apparently fearless athlete will discover corners of Mexico otherwise unreachable by land. Follow his challenge navigating through the Gulf and find out what happens along the way.

programme.title: Speed Catamarans GC32 - Episode 6
programme.desc: For its sixth season, the ultra-high performance one design catamarans, once again visited five top venues across the world. Each location selected particularly for its ideal weather conditions - stable winds and flat waters - perfect for the nimble GC32s to fly across the water at speeds of over 30 knots. Earlier in 2019, intensive discussions and decisions took place within the teams with many deciding to focus their efforts for the upcoming season, on the GC32 Racing Tour. This season the tour welcomed some new teams as well as many familiar regular GC32 crews. In total 12 teams from 9 different counties came together to take part in the 6th GC32 Racing Tour. Amongst them, some of the most well-known professional sailors in the world.

programme.title: H2O Racing: Aquabike World Championship - GP Spain - Ski
International Canoe Federation World Cup - Sprint 3 World Championships Szeged
programme.desc: Welcome to the Canoe Sprint World Championships 2019 celebrated in Szeged, Hungary! Today there are about 1,200 athletes racing from approximately 98 nations, meaning this is the biggest World Championships canoe sprint racing has ever seen. We're about to witness the fastest paddlers on the planet battle it out for medals, for World Championship glory, and to qualify for their country at the Tokyo 2020 Olympic Games. Enjoy the best moments at Szeged on the 2019 Sprint World Championships.

programme.title: International Canoe Federation World Cup - Slalom 1 World Cup Ljubljana
programme.desc: Ljubljana is the chosen scenery for the Slalom World Cup. The slovenian capital will bring the top kayakers who will navigate the whitewater course passing through a series of combination of upstream and downstream gates. The fastest to achieve this will become the champion of the World Cup. Find out now what will happen in Ljubljana in the exciting Slalom World Cup!

programme.title: Event Rider Masters - Wiesbaden

Be part of the best moments of the competition in the 2019 edition.

programme.desc: Welcome to Salzburg!The second leg of the Western European League inside the FEI Dressage World Cup takes place in the Austrian city. We are ready to see some of the very best horse and rider combinations in the sport and immerse in the city Mozart grew up in. Celebrating its 35th year, Dressage World Cup is the most distinguished individual competition in the international dressage calendar, rising at four leagues across the world: Western Europe, Central Europe, North America and Asia Pacific. The Western European League gathers together Europe's nine best dressage competitions, and, despite these challenging times, Salzburg has proved to be a safe destination where the exquisiteness of dressage will feel just like at home. Follow the Fei Dressage World Cup from Salzburg to find out what rider takes the upper hand in this competition.

programme.title: Cavalli a Roma - Best Moments
programme.desc: Cavalli a Roma mixes tradition with innovation, delighting the public with show jumping competitions, equestrian art and traditional shows that grasp both adults and children's attention. Now, on HorseTV you can revive all the emotions and best impressions of the 2020 edition.

programme.title: Longines Global Champions Tour - Episode 5 - Stockholm
programme.desc: Peder Fredricson is standing in the top of the Longines Global Champions Tour 2021 rankings this year, however things can change quickly during the fifth leg in Stockholm. The Global Champions Tour Grand Prix of Stockholm disputed in the Olympic Stadium will prove to be a test like no other.Watch the 2021 LGCT Stockholm competition.

programme.title: Global Champions League - Episode 5 - Stockholm
programme.desc: Stockholm is hosting the fifth leg of the GCL 2021 edition. The Swedish capital has set the Olympic Stadium as the chosen venue for this clash of titans. Previously, Paris Panthers had its first win of the tournament in Valkenswaard. Will they be able to repeat this success in Stockholm?Watch the best moments of the CSI5* 1.55M GCL 2021 edition in its fifth leg.

programme.title: Sunshine Tour - Episode 6 - GP Suzuki
programme.desc: Dehesa Montenmedio farewells this October Tour with the Grand Prix Suzuki. The 1.55m circuit designed by Javier Trenor has seen 6 pairs of riders and horses achieve the jump-off, but the challenge is just starting. Riders rush through the CSIO3* course, and results are unpredictable. Watch the best moments of the GP Suzuki celebrated in Spain 2021.

programme.title: Jumping International de Dinard - Tropicana Derby of Dinard
programme.desc: The mythical Tropicana Derby is one of the categories inside the Jumping International de Dinard, and it offers a combination of traditional and natural fences over a particularly long distance of 1100m that will bring both horse and rider to their limit. Relive the best moments of Dinards Tropicana Derby with a jumping height over 1.45m.

programme.title: Campus Life Experience - Episode 6
programme.desc: In this new episode, we first realize the vet check to determine whether the horse is in good physical condition to take part in the competition. Once everything is fine with our horses, we check our rider's boots and then get a good night sleep as we will have to wake up at 6 for Manuel's class.

programme.title: Campus Life Experience - Episode 7
programme.desc: The educational program that lasted a week is finally reaching its end. Participants had their cell phones taken away and were given food, clothes and taught how to take care of their horses. Now, they are sad their adventure is over but share with us their final impressions for the week.

programme.title: Event Rider Masters - Millstreet
programme.desc: For the fifth leg of the Event Rider Masters we head to the 'Land of the Horse' for the first time. Millstreet in Ireland is the chosen venue this time, and the Cross-Country Course in the adjoining Drishane Castle Demesne has quickly established itself as a favourite amongst the best riders of the world. Be part of the best moments of the competition at Millstreet.

programme.title: German High Goal Polo Championship - German High Goal Polo Championship
programme.desc: The German Polo Tour has been the top polo league in Germany since 2010. Now, rivalling teams will have to compete in the Prussian & Country Club Berlin-Brandenburg for the Cup. The final between Carfactory and Riller & Schmauck is now on. Enjoy the competition and follow the top level of german polo in Horse TV.

programme.title: Jumping International Bordeaux - Grand Prix Land Rover
programme.desc: The CSI5*W Grand Prix Land Rover Trophée is one of the most awaited competitions in the Jumping International de Bordeaux. Riders will have to show their perseverance, effort and speed in the obstacle course in order to get a spot in the podium.Relieve the best moments of the Grand Prix Land Rover 2019 edition.

programme.title: FEI Rides Magazine - Episode 2: Stories from the Stud

programme.desc: This week Ride travels back in time on the UK’s waterways aboard one of the last remaining horse drawn Barges.
